/* USAGE */

$ruby main.rb -u http://store.steampowered.com/***/

If the title on this URL is discounted, output is like this:

<a href="http://store.steampowered.com/***/" target="_blank">Game Title</a> $x.xx -> $y.yy (zz%off) 


Or with text file mode, you can easily execute many URL.

$ruby main.rb -f url.list

Each URL in list must be splitted return.